Reduce, TP Rs 1680

Management meet key takeaways,

(1) Gen AI adoption among enterprises will be gradual and requires services;

(2) service providers will capture a part of the value from Gen AI adoption;

(3) Gen AI will be a net tailwind for services, but need to capture new opportunities;

(4) Gen AI deflation will be higher in software development and select BPO segments;

(5) HCLT’s software business will not be significantly impacted by Gen AI;

(6) AI agents require human intervention.
